data.description: Don't miss this charming ranch home that has been well maintained and ready for a new owner. Main level has three bedrooms and one full bath. The kitchen has ample cabinet space with a breakfast bar and a dine in area. There is an open living room and formal dining area. The basement is partially finished for an extra living space and has great storage and another partial bathroom. The attic has great potential to create a unique finished space.
